# grapher_ineq_exterior_smoke.numos — Phase 10D. Plot x^2+y^2>1: the solution is
# the EXTERIOR of the unit circle (G=lhs-rhs>0). Proves the region direction flips
# with the operator. Warning-only (no golden); NOT CI-gated.
log "ineq exterior: start"
wait 200
open_app Grapher
wait 60
key down
key enter
key x
key ^
key 2
key right
key +
key y
key ^
key 2
key right
key gt
key 1
key enter
wait 80
key graph
wait 60
key zoom
key zoom
wait 120
screenshot out/grapher_ineq_exterior_smoke.ppm
assert_app Grapher
log "ineq exterior: x^2+y^2>1 shaded"
